## 📊 High-Performance Grid
The grid has been updated for maximum audit fidelity:
- **Columns**: `Ref#`, [Date](file:///g:/My%20Drive/RoboLedger%20-%20NEW/src/parsers_raw/RBCChequingParser.js#622-626), [Description](file:///g:/My%20Drive/AutoBookkeeping/AutoBookkeeping-V4/src/pages/txn-import-v5-v2.js#5431-5433), [Debit](file:///g:/My%20Drive/AutoBookkeeping/AutoBookkeeping-V4/src/pages/txn-import-v5-v2.js#2225-2249), [Credit](file:///g:/My%20Drive/RoboLedger%20-%20NEW/src/parsers_raw/RBCChequingParser.js#627-631), [Balance](file:///g:/My%20Drive/RoboLedger%20-%20NEW/src/types/coa.ts#57-58), [Category](file:///g:/My%20Drive/RoboLedger%20-%20NEW/src/ui/pro/app.js#122-128).
